{"tid":751372,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"前女友話要專心讀書所以分手","createTime":"2018-07-21T20:47:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T03:58:17.000Z","uid":168547,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9171da5acafb1a764c54968911383e7ff77fd740","tid":751372,"uid":168547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T20:47:37.000Z","msg":"同初戀前女友分手都分左3年幾<br />\n最近唸翻起當年分手嘅原因<br />\n佢突然間話 要專心讀書<br />\n本身都無咩爭執 感情體落去仲好地地<br />\n有時一齊放下學 偶爾出個街<br />\n然後有一日佢突然whatsapp我話<br />\n不如分手啦 要專心讀書<br />\n個一刻真係呆左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然事後都有算挽回過 但係都失敗左<br />\n事後過左年幾 我透過朋友留意下佢<br />\n佢成績好似無進步過 仲費左<br />\n所以究竟係咩原因所以分手呢<br />\n致今仍然百思不得其解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\nps我地分左手之後佢起碼半年後先有新男朋友<br />\n所以應該不是green吧"},{"pid":"9d368d33bcaafbf8d9776cfdc71ec031edda754c","tid":751372,"uid":136186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T20:48:27.000Z","msg":"帽事"},{"pid":"9314d61616dcec670f6b17ea91c028a44e16ff23","tid":751372,"uid":152437,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T20:50:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3872c489dcb7dbee28919b3a99d775a997cc6466","tid":751372,"uid":161537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T21:19:40.000Z","msg":"無啦啦做乜諗呢啲嘢<br />\n唔愛你咪總結哂所有藉口囉，完。"},{"pid":"bf5e0449de2ad1836bdf5659482e37074ac8d1b6","tid":751372,"uid":36696,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T21:21:45.000Z","msg":"如果真係專心讀書就唔會識另一條仔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"218658ab0768e9be6f097b3d10c16bf989641a20","tid":751372,"uid":171025,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T21:25:52.000Z","msg":"我以前都試過<br />\n嗰陣大家都讀緊中三<br />\n有一日我女朋友同我講佢想專心準備DSE唔想拍拖<br />\n我嗰陣當然好唔開心 <br />\n一年幾之後我喺又一城見返佢<br />\n佢同一個男仔拖住手行街<br />\n見個男仔都幾7下所以讀書應該都幾勁<br />\nAnyway嗰陣係幾難受<br />\n過多一年之後DSE放榜<br />\n我個ex做咗狀元入咗唔記得邊間讀醫<br />\n嗰陣其實好為佢驕傲都好想親口同佢講聲恭喜曬<br />\n但係都無機會"},{"pid":"0719d9715003ced7b8ba3ad56e1b53b5670f4b20","tid":751372,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T21:41:27.000Z","msg":"雞"},{"pid":"dd2414d11a866410e252bb31c12fb77b364f670c","tid":751372,"uid":192078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T23:08:21.000Z","msg":"過去嘅嘢講來做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de6ff4ed422c8903550d93fa34f25fbc98b86a0b","tid":751372,"uid":131369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T00:31:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> green左幾年都唔知"},{"pid":"aed48dc6aee236fcf62d4f05fc08b54388ee2904","tid":751372,"uid":130298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T00:36:47.000Z","msg":"唔係帽都係鍾意左第2個，利申試過"},{"pid":"1243ce7ad7fb107ac931817b6ef5fa257be1c789","tid":751372,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T01:49:35.000Z","msg":"蠢到咁唔飛你飛邊個呀？"},{"pid":"54ce6364fbcf709cc743e84982b1f8182642fc7c","tid":751372,"uid":183438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T03:04:40.000Z","msg":"同你分手之後同新男朋友一齊之間個段時間，你肯定佢無識其他人？"},{"pid":"abd302c97d852d251201dfec25cb37e34f682be5","tid":751372,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T03:05:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只不過分手個刻佢想追條仔唔要佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33fa3b30d1245168336074264a65aec01c53a3fa","tid":751372,"uid":185421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T03:50:02.000Z","msg":"都係自私嘅人所為。。。<br />\n我明白你因爲我都比自私嘅人hurt完。。。"},{"pid":"b70f3d2c37fb1d80d83022573ac1cd480cc742eb","tid":751372,"uid":168547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1243ce7ad7fb107ac931817b6ef5fa257be1c789","tid":751372,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T01:49:35.000Z","msg":"蠢到咁唔飛你飛邊個呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T03:52:06.000Z","msg":"抵飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7764328dce6cea6925f3d57d9a78523b442205b","tid":751372,"uid":38675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T03:58:17.000Z","msg":"其實你自己都答咗<br />\n駛乜要人幫你分析啫<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}